  "prompt": "How widely accepted are credit cards at small businesses and restaurants in Barbados?",
  "response": "In Barbados, credit cards are widely accepted at most restaurants, hotels, larger stores, and tourist-oriented businesses. Visa and Mastercard are the most commonly accepted cards. However, some smaller, local businesses and restaurants, particularly in more rural areas, may prefer cash or only accept local debit cards. It's always a good idea to carry some cash as a backup, especially when visiting smaller establishments or local markets.",
